Usage: hm_test.exe <path to directory> <command> <argument>

Commands include:
create - create a number of files in the specified directory
Example: hm_test.exe c:\directory create <number of files>

encrypt - simulate encryption (overwrite a file with something different)
Example: hm_test.exe c:\directory encrypt <number of files>

Each file will be 1 megabyte in size. 

In the case of 'create', the file will be filled with the number 0.
In the case of 'encrypt', the file will be filled with the number 1.
